<tr>
<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="padding-left:0;padding-right:0;">
<div style="padding:0em 0.75em;">Daughters</div>
</th>
<td class="navbox-list navbox-even" style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li>Margaret Stewart, married <a href="/wiki/John_of_Islay,_Lord_of_the_Isles" title="John of Islay, Lord of the Isles">John of Islay, Lord of the Isles</a></li>
<li>Marjory Stewart, married (1) <a href="/wiki/John_Dunbar,_Earl_of_Moray" title="John Dunbar, Earl of Moray">John Dunbar, Earl of Moray</a> (2) Alexander Keith</li>
<li>Johanna Stewart, married (1) Sir John Keith (2) Sir <a href="/wiki/John_Lyon_(lord_of_Glamis)" class="mw-redirect" title="John Lyon (lord of Glamis)">John Lyon (lord of Glamis)</a> (3) 1384 Sir James Sandilands</li>
<li>Isabella Stewart married (1) <a href="/wiki/James_Douglas,_2nd_Earl_of_Douglas" title="James Douglas, 2nd Earl of Douglas">James Douglas, 2nd Earl of Douglas</a> (2) David Edmondstone</li>
<li>Katherine Stewart, married Sir Robert Logan of Grugar and Restalrig, <a href="/wiki/Lord_High_Admiral_of_Scotland" class="mw-redirect" title="Lord High Admiral of Scotland">Lord High Admiral of Scotland</a></li>
<li>Elizabeth Stewart, married Sir <a href="/wiki/Thomas_de_la_Hay" title="Thomas de la Hay">Thomas Hay</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Lord_High_Constable_of_Scotland" title="Lord High Constable of Scotland">Lord High Constable of Scotland</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
